name: OG Kush
description: A classic indica-dominant strain known for its relaxing effects. Features a complex aroma with notes of fuel, skunk, and spice.

name: Blue Dream
description: A sativa-dominant hybrid that provides balanced, full-body relaxation with gentle cerebral invigoration. Sweet berry aroma.

name: Pineapple Express
description: A potent vape cartridge with a taste of fresh apple and mango. Offers a long-lasting energetic buzz perfect for productive afternoons.

name: Midnight Mint
description: Rich dark chocolate infused with cool mint and full-spectrum cannabis oil. Each piece contains 10mg of THC.
